      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Critical Errors Dashboard (Phase 2B)\n\nThis dashboard focuses on **actionable errors** that require investigation:\n- mcp-server.service failures (repeated exit codes)\n- logging-e2e-check.service startup failures\n- Other service-specific critical events\n\n**Filtered out**: VSCode debug logs, DNS warnings, Node.js trace warnings (low-value noise)\n\n**Goal**: Signal-to-noise ratio improvement from 27% â†’ 90% actionable errors"
